born villain is a short film directed by actor shia labeouf in collaboration with marilyn manson . it was released on august 28 , 2011 , during its inaugural screening , at the l.a. silent theater . produced as an accompaniment to the born villain album , the film was intended as the record 's promotional " trailer " . the music heard in the video is the song " &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; the path of misery " , a track from born villain .